data.description: Updated cottage full of charm. From the early 1900's but lots of updates including new roof, vinyl siding, water heater, deck, insulation, laminate floors, updated - bathroom and woodstove, 2 beds and full bath downstairs. 1 huge bedroom and full bath upstairs, Big country kitchen and huge utility/laundry room plus office. Enjoy the country life on the porch swing or the 20' x 28' deck. Has detached oversized garage and carport.
